  "title": "Union",
  "root": "",
  "statement": "The \\emph{union} of $A$ and $B$, denoted $A \\cup B$, is the set of all\nelements belonging to at least one of the two sets:\n\\[\nA \\cup B \\;=\\; \\{\\, x \\mid x \\in A \\lor x \\in B \\,\\}.\n\\]",
